reviewText:
Real glad I can watch this great season again with my family, Thank You very much

Vicky Ross :) I recommend this person any day.

The video is great, watch the late Dale Earnhardt win his first Daytona 500 on his 20th try. You will also see Jeff Gordon get his 13th win and tie Richard Petty with the most wins in one season. You'll see much more. If you are a big Nascar fan, you should see this video.
